18#ifndef _LVM_FILTER_H
19#define _LVM_FILTER_H
20
21#include "config.h"
22
23#include <sys/stat.h>
24
25#ifdef linux
26# define MAJOR(dev) ((dev & 0xfff00) >> 8)
27# define MINOR(dev) ((dev & 0xff) | ((dev >> 12) & 0xfff00))
28# define MKDEV(ma,mi) ((mi & 0xff) | (ma << 8) | ((mi & ~0xff) << 12))
29#else
30# define MAJOR(x) major((x))
31# define MINOR(x) minor((x))
32# define MKDEV(x,y) makedev((x),(y))
33#endif
34
35struct dev_filter *lvm_type_filter_create(const char *proc,
36 const struct config_node *cn);
37
38void lvm_type_filter_destroy(struct dev_filter *f);
39
40int md_major(void);
41int blkext_major(void);
42int max_partitions(int major);
43
44int dev_subsystem_part_major(const struct device *dev);
45const char *dev_subsystem_name(const struct device *dev);
46
47#endif
